# JavaScript/Node.js Conventions

- Formatter: **Prettier** (default config)
- Indent: 2 spaces
- Variables: `const` / `let` (never `var`)
- Modules: ESM (`import/export`) where possible, CJS for legacy compat
- Package manager: **pnpm** (never npm or yarn)

## VulnShop Specifics

- App entrypoint: `labs/vulnshop/index.js`
- Routes go in `labs/vulnshop/src/routes/` (when modularized)
- Mark vulnerabilities: `// VULN: [category] - [description]`
- Document in `labs/vulnshop/vulns/VULNERABILITIES.md`
- Tests in `labs/vulnshop/tests/test_vulns.js`
- Lock file: `pnpm-lock.yaml`

## Testing

```bash
cd labs/vulnshop && pnpm test
```
